---
---
<section>
  <div class="section-label">Who It's For</div>
  <h2>Every role in the<br/><em>fabric value chain.</em></h2>

  <div class="personas-row">
    <div class="persona-card">
      <div class="persona-icon" style="background: rgba(200,133,58,0.1); color: var(--amber);">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 7H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v10a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z"/><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="persona-name">Vendor</div>
      <p class="persona-desc">List your entire catalog — single bolts or bulk groups. Showcase trends. Clear dead stock with direct buyer connections.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="persona-card">
      <div class="persona-icon" style="background: rgba(90,130,200,0.1); color: #8faae0;">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6 2 3 6v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V6l-3-4z"/><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/><path d="M16 10a4 4 0 0 1-8 0"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="persona-name">Buyer</div>
      <p class="persona-desc">Source fabrics at scale. Discover dead stock opportunities and connect directly with vendors for offline deals.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="persona-card">
      <div class="persona-icon" style="background: rgba(130,180,130,0.1); color: #90c890;">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 19l7-7 3 3-7 7-3-3z"/><path d="M18 13l-1.5-7.5L2 2l3.5 14.5L13 18l5-5z"/><path d="M2 2l7.586 7.586"/><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="2"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="persona-name">Designer</div>
      <p class="persona-desc">Generate fabric variations without prints. Visualize final looks virtually. Source unique materials from verified vendors.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="persona-card">
      <div class="persona-icon" style="background: rgba(200,133,58,0.07); color: var(--muted);">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="7"/><polyline points="8.21 13.89 7 23 12 20 17 23 15.79 13.88"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="persona-name">Operator</div>
      <p class="persona-desc">Manage inventory, coordinate logistics, and oversee stock clearance operations across the platform.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .personas-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .personas-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
</style>
